  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2396660/extras/aec6d46b80183c87173e7da1b283a658.avif?t=1744896807\" width=600 height=396 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2396660/extras/70c72bb409dae9b5e7d7a5326391afcf.avif?t=1744896807\" width=616 height=200 /></span>Nova, the once celebrated and now infamous pirate known as ‘La Belladonna’, has been unjustly accused, clapped in chains, and thrown to rot in a cell. Someone out there is sinking ships, and the whole world seems to believe it’s <i>you</i>...</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The only way to clear your name is to unmask the real culprit—no easy feat, when you’re a fugitive with the whole Arcomare Alliance sailing in pursuit.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Thankfully, you are not alone...</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Your <strong>best friend Xander</strong> has had your back since childhood. But will his loyalty to the pirates get in the way of your friendship... and of the feelings that are budding between you?</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The <strong>seductive Don Lorenzo</strong> argued to have you imprisoned, but why? As you learn the complex truth of his motives, can you grow from enemies to sincere friends, or even lovers?</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2396660/extras/1728be060e3a2b0c226cd70508fe7b85.avif?t=1744896807\" width=616 height=200 /></span>Test your skills and strategic prowess as you take on rival vessels in swashbuckling combat! Evade, blast your cannons, and board their ships to give them a piece of your mind. Buoyed by your feats, earn notoriety and unlock new boons to blaze your way to victory!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Features:</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Real time ship battles</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Pirate boons for long term upgrades</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Shipyard for short term upgrades</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Plenty of prestige and gold to collect</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2396660/extras/1e8b9d9553900a04c0e3d961e893bdd9.poster.avif?t=1744896807\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2396660/extras/1e8b9d9553900a04c0e3d961e893bdd9.webm?t=1744896807\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2396660/extras/1e8b9d9553900a04c0e3d961e893bdd9.mp4?t=1744896807\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >With easy to learn but hard to master combat, your strategic skills will be challenged!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >But fear not - if you prefer easier battles, that can be changed in the settings.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2396660/extras/ecf0171a60e91fd831aaedb22510ce55.avif?t=1744896807\" width=616 height=200 /></span>Can you find the secrets behind your cursed fate and save yourself from the gallows? Meet a captivating cast of fellow pirates, minstrels, witches and political adversaries as you piece together the mystery and magic behind your false imprisonment.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2396660/extras/4c2450c6bee466a1aaf91b5c073d13ac.poster.avif?t=1744896807\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2396660/extras/4c2450c6bee466a1aaf91b5c073d13ac.webm?t=1744896807\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2396660/extras/4c2450c6bee466a1aaf91b5c073d13ac.mp4?t=1744896807\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2396660/extras/aec6d46b80183c87173e7da1b283a658.avif?t=1744896807\" width=600 height=396 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2396660/extras/70c72bb409dae9b5e7d7a5326391afcf.avif?t=1744896807\" width=616 height=200 /></span>Nova, the once celebrated and now infamous pirate known as ‘La Belladonna’, has been unjustly accused, clapped in chains, and thrown to rot in a cell. Someone out there is sinking ships, and the whole world seems to believe it’s <i>you</i>...</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The only way to clear your name is to unmask the real culprit—no easy feat, when you’re a fugitive with the whole Arcomare Alliance sailing in pursuit.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Thankfully, you are not alone...</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Your <strong>best friend Xander</strong> has had your back since childhood. But will his loyalty to the pirates get in the way of your friendship... and of the feelings that are budding between you?</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The <strong>seductive Don Lorenzo</strong> argued to have you imprisoned, but why? As you learn the complex truth of his motives, can you grow from enemies to sincere friends, or even lovers?</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2396660/extras/1728be060e3a2b0c226cd70508fe7b85.avif?t=1744896807\" width=616 height=200 /></span>Test your skills and strategic prowess as you take on rival vessels in swashbuckling combat! Evade, blast your cannons, and board their ships to give them a piece of your mind. Buoyed by your feats, earn notoriety and unlock new boons to blaze your way to victory!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Features:</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Real time ship battles</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Pirate boons for long term upgrades</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Shipyard for short term upgrades</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Plenty of prestige and gold to collect</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2396660/extras/1e8b9d9553900a04c0e3d961e893bdd9.poster.avif?t=1744896807\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2396660/extras/1e8b9d9553900a04c0e3d961e893bdd9.webm?t=1744896807\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2396660/extras/1e8b9d9553900a04c0e3d961e893bdd9.mp4?t=1744896807\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >With easy to learn but hard to master combat, your strategic skills will be challenged!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >But fear not - if you prefer easier battles, that can be changed in the settings.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2396660/extras/ecf0171a60e91fd831aaedb22510ce55.avif?t=1744896807\" width=616 height=200 /></span>Can you find the secrets behind your cursed fate and save yourself from the gallows? Meet a captivating cast of fellow pirates, minstrels, witches and political adversaries as you piece together the mystery and magic behind your false imprisonment.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2396660/extras/4c2450c6bee466a1aaf91b5c073d13ac.poster.avif?t=1744896807\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2396660/extras/4c2450c6bee466a1aaf91b5c073d13ac.webm?t=1744896807\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2396660/extras/4c2450c6bee466a1aaf91b5c073d13ac.mp4?t=1744896807\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
